---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="MDK.GURU - one person and seven AI agents studio. Ilya Chernyak.">
  <div class="pt-24 min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4"><span class="gradient-text">About</span></h1>
      <p class="text-text-muted mb-12 text-lg">One person. Seven agents. No office.</p>
      <div class="space-y-8 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Who am I</h2>
          <p>Ilya Chernyak, entrepreneur from Russia. Three businesses: electronics, vape shops, equipment rental. Two kids, sailing, padel tennis, and a constant drive to automate everything.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">What is MDK.GURU</h2>
          <p>Not an agency. Not a dev shop. An experiment: can one person with a team of AI agents do what usually requires a staff?</p>
          <p class="mt-3">Content pipeline, sales analytics, competitor monitoring, design - all done by my 5 agents powered by OpenClaw. 24/7. No salaries. No days off.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Why this site</h2>
          <p>Sharing practice. Cases, mistakes, tools. Everything I learn goes here. No fluff, no overpriced courses.</p>
          <p class="mt-3">If you're an entrepreneur wondering how AI agents can work in real business - you're in the right place.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-12 p-6 rounded-xl border border-accent-purple/20 bg-accent-purple/5 text-center">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Follow the experiment</p>
          <a href="https://t.me/mdkguru" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-2 rounded-lg bg-accent-purple text-white text-sm hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">@mdkguru on Telegram →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
